-- ALTER VIEW kpivis.dim_tft_coaching
-- AS
SELECT
[CICLO_TERRITORIO]
,[COACH_ROW_ID_TERRITORIO]
,[COACH_MUDID]
,[COACH_CICLO]
,[COACH_CICLO_ATUAL]
,[COACH_TERRITORIO_GRI]
,[TOTAL_COACHING]
,[TFT_ABATER]
,[MOTIVO_ABATER]
,[TOTAL_ABATER]
,[TFT_NAO_ABATER]
,[MOTIVO_NAO_ABATER]
,[TOTAL_NAO_ABATER]
,[PERC_COACHING]
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://gsksynapseaccount.dfs.core.windows.net/gskoutputfiles/KPI Visitacao/dimensao_tft_coaching.parquet',
        FORMAT='PARQUET'
    ) WITH (
[CICLO_TERRITORIO]			VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[COACH_ROW_ID_TERRITORIO]	VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[COACH_MUDID]				VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[COACH_CICLO]				VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[COACH_CICLO_ATUAL]		VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[COACH_TERRITORIO_GRI]		VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TOTAL_COACHING]			VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TFT_ABATER]				VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[MOTIVO_ABATER]			VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TOTAL_ABATER]				VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TFT_NAO_ABATER]			VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[MOTIVO_NAO_ABATER]		VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TOTAL_NAO_ABATER]			VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[PERC_COACHING]			VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
    ) AS ROW
